name: Raining Humans
description: I took my cat, Frizzi, on a sunny Wednesday picnic. He then got sunburned. Aside from that, he surely enjoyed the biggest sandy toilet in Planet Wau-Wau. Suddenly, a storm swiped the entire seashore, we were lucky cause Purple the turtle invited us to his fancy igloo. As the storm vanished, I saw people falling from the sky like raindrops. There might be a rainbow if only we waited for a moment, but we were in a hurry back home to see our favorite cartoon on Petflix. We can't wait for the next Wednesday to go back there as we already made a promise with Purple the turtle to have a spaghetti feast at his fancy igloo.
